{"tid":1241383,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"網上 \"Tap n Go\" App 訂閱蘋果動新聞教學 (夠11歲就用得)","createTime":"2019-06-18T16:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T06:56:54.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cc2b677e139045a9e10edaa21990e1d90e62c162","tid":1241383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T16:30:07.000Z","msg":"網上 &quot;Tap n Go&quot; App 訂閱蘋果動新聞教學 (夠11歲就用得)<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n啱啱用 &quot;Tap n Go&quot; App 成功訂閱咗 蘋果動新聞   (夠11歲就用得)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oq1Xhg8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOq1Xhg8.png&h=b987fceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n原來唔太難<br />\n<br />\n首先 download and install 咗 Tap n Go App<br />\n<br />\n呢度<br />\n <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hktpayment.tapngo&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.hktpayment.tapngo%26hl%3Den&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=7fca3f6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.hktpayment.tapngo&amp;hl=en</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/blClJZ2sHQSnK95cDqXVYY3gIrcW4XzZzWa_CdhoMV1ghZVoUXoie8OVXXH7gb2VGcw=s180-rw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FblClJZ2sHQSnK95cDqXVYY3gIrcW4XzZzWa_CdhoMV1ghZVoUXoie8OVXXH7gb2VGcw%3Ds180-rw&h=107e93a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住呢度做嚟啟動張 網上 mastercard 預付 card<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tapngo.com.hk/chi/apply.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tapngo.com.hk%2Fchi%2Fapply.html&d=HhKtR2wUfRZLc9nBt5dK8BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=ce5c6d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tapngo.com.hk/chi/apply.html</a><br />\n<br />\n跟住去 7-11 或 Circle K 增值<br />\n<br />\n增值完就可以去 蘋果訂閱 網上webpage 用呢張網上預付 mastercard 嚟訂閱<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩問題可以係度問,  識既我會盡答, 因為啱啱先開完張卡, 增值, 訂閱埋.<br />\n(原來喺 youtube 既 Super Chat 都用到, 啱啱試埋, work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n其他識答既巴絲都可以答既,  互相幫忙, 唔該晒.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港加油"},{"pid":"2088d5f5ac9da44c4efa3c6f3ae458ecf91276ae","tid":1241383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e86ae970dabd406d53b7fdc234bfd8269b92cf37","tid":1241383,"uid":198800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-18T17:54:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20b9913744fc644325ec032ac1182e7a548555d8","tid":1241383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T01:08:28.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"67285b34ae8b325229362f353fdce4c0eb446a40","tid":1241383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"7月4日下午起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/campaign/images/welovehk_title3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcampaign%2Fimages%2Fwelovehk_title3.png&h=77a81a71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FMxv7br.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFMxv7br.jpg&h=347a307e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3bad7ae23f474fd9ebf4666ee64375527f4714e0","tid":1241383,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T02:30:20.000Z","msg":"即係將張t and g 當信用卡咁pay??<br />\n利申用開t and g"},{"pid":"61c8735da0d525a3f2c83dfd690fa191bf71492b","tid":1241383,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3bad7ae23f474fd9ebf4666ee64375527f4714e0","tid":12